                                   Introduction
                                   ~~~~~~~~~~~~
    --------------------------------------------------------------------------
          This manual assumes you are familiar with the RISC OS desktop. You
          may want to read the Welcome Guide and the User Guide#url
          http://acorn.riscos.com/riscos3/37/37DiscImage/Manuals/Manual/BOOKB/
          BOOK_3.HTM> that come with your RISC OS system.
          You may also want to read this introduction to RISC OS.
    --------------------------------------------------------------------------
    InsertIcon inserts sprites into either the normal spritepool or the
    priority sprite pool introduced with RISC OS Select. It can also replace
    the toolsprites.
    --------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                                                      Previous
                                                                          Next
    ==========================================================================

                                   Installation
                                   ~~~~~~~~~~~~
    --------------------------------------------------------------------------
      è   Download the program.
      è   The program is compressed into a Zip archive. Decompress it using
          e.g. SparkFS or Sparkplug#URL
          http://pilling.users.netlink.co.uk/free.html>.
      è   Copy the decompressed application, and any other files in the
          archive, to a place on your harddisc.
      è   That is it - you have installed InsertIcn.
    --------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                                                      Previous
                                                                          Next
    ==========================================================================

                                     Starting
                                     ~~~~~~~~
    --------------------------------------------------------------------------
          Use the interactive help to get help on specific icons and
          menuitems.
    --------------------------------------------------------------------------
    Use
    Double click on the !InsertIcn icon in the filer window. This will put an
    icon the iconbar.
    To insert sprites into a sprite pool drag the file containing those

                                                                        Page 1
    sprites to the iconbar icon. If shift is pressed during the drag, a
    configure window will open otherwise the sprites will be joined
    imediately.
    NOTE: Only files with filetype Sprite (FF9) are accepted.

    Configration
    The configuration window lets you choose where the sprites will be
    inserted and you can also make InsertIcon force a redraw after inserting
    those sprites.
    The Target Priority pool will only work on RISC OS Select.
    Click on Insert to insert all sprites from the file into the selected
    sprite pool.
    --------------------------------------------------------------------------
